398, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"planning\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"the mega\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon budgets\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Measures to slash emissions were built into plans from the start.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Measures\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"emissions\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as athletes seek ways to shave milliseconds off their times, Paris organizers sought not just big carbon savings by building just one competition venue specifically for the Games, but smaller ones, too.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2144553943510378e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"milliseconds\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"their times\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"big carbon savings\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"just one competition\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic cauldron used electricity and LED spotlights to give the impression of being ablaze.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic cauldron\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"electricity\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"LED spotlights\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"the impression\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That made it 300 times less polluting than if it had burned gas.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gas\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even Olympic medals included recycled materials, with each embedded with a reused chunk of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled materials\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"a reused chunk\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Electricity powered 98.4 percent of the Games' energy needs, and organizers said a purchasing agreement they signed with power supplier EDF ensured it was all solar- or wind-generated.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Electricity\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"98.4 percent\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' energy needs\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"a purchasing agreement\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"power supplier\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"EDF\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plant-based hot dogs and other vegetarian offerings less carbon-intensive than meat dishes accounted for 40 percent of the food that spectators ate, and the carbon footprint of meals served to Games workers and volunteers was half that of the typical French meal, organizers said.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Plant-based hot dogs\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"other vegetarian offerings\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"meat dishes\", \