 2593, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP In selling 12.1 million tickets, Paris set attendance records.\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2728, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2144553943510378e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/CFP\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"12.1 million tickets\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"attendance records\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But transporting spectators to the French capital and to events came at an unexpectedly large carbon cost.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2785}, {\"ngram\": \"the French capital\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2807}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"an unexpectedly large carbon cost\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Transport had been expected to account for about one-third of Paris' carbon footprint, but organizers said it ended up accounting for 53 percent.\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2927, \"end\": 2932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2144553943510378e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Transport\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"53 percent\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just over 66 percent of spectators came from France.\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3057, \"end\": 3063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999966803471201, \"rank\": 3.014595525492965e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Just over 66 percent\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 21 percent came from elsewhere in Europe, and another 12 percent came from further afield, led by ticket-holders from the United States, Brazil and Canada.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3197, \"end\": 3210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999989186627707, \"rank\": 1.0813383137648338e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3212, \"end\": 3218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9999999811161617, \"rank\": 9.949993135360328e-09, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999503593257, \"rank\": 4.96316550766377e-08, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than 21 percent\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3085}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"another 12 percent\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"ticket-holders\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For spectators who took long-haul flights, the 